{"type": "article", "id": 25436, "title": "石英石搭配双色玻璃的边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070211503404xJu3nNpGMmvSlA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这两张小的边桌由英国设计工作室 Kukka Studio 设计，他们使用了白色的石英石和双色玻璃两种材料。双色玻璃产自德国，玻璃上柔和的渐变色会随着人的行动而改变，很特别。白色的石英石源于以色列，作为桌子的底座和衬托背景，两者都使用了非常规整的几何图形，有对比和平衡的作用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150325iTNGX7MUVQO3jmI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115033uJTo7hb2fY95FAtn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80021368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115033onaPs9EmNLKHw45d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71474359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115034tprT79W4OYcqimsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115034syHf7XMWIJVSRFqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}